@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bhbirg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.17)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.40 - tmp + 0.72)) * (tmp * wp.cos(tmp + 0.00)))
    v2 = 0.26
    tmp = 0.25
    v2 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(0.27)
    data[tid] = v0
